243
00:15:07,130 --> 00:15:08,000
Betul ke?

244
00:15:08,000 --> 00:15:09,040
Sudah tentu.

245
00:15:09,350 --> 00:15:10,700
Sebaik sahaja saya memergokinya melukis secara rahsia,

246
00:15:10,700 --> 00:15:12,370
Saya telah merampas semua peralatan melukisnya.

247
00:15:12,370 --> 00:15:13,580
Jadi dia mengambil batu

248
00:15:13,770 --> 00:15:15,040
