Li Wanzhe!

321
00:20:13,010 --> 00:20:13,940
Apa?

322
00:20:14,120 --> 00:20:16,180
Ibu awak suruh awak turun dan tolong!

323
00:20:16,180 --> 00:20:18,380
Kami ada ramai pelanggan hari ini,
