354
00:21:46,720 --> 00:21:49,040
Anak perempuannya dan dia sentiasa bertengkar.

355
00:21:49,040 --> 00:21:50,700
Itu hanyalah kebiasaan harian mereka.

356
00:21:50,960 --> 00:21:52,630
Tidur siang dan malam.

357
00:21:53,040 --> 00:21:54,410
-Awak orang tua.
-Awak betul-betul...

358
00:21:54,410 --> 00:21:56,460
Macam mana aku nak
tulis lagu macam ni?

359
00:21:56,460 --> 00:21:57,400
Tuan.

360
00:21:58,300 --> 00:21:59,220
Berapakah harga gula-gula itu?

361
00:21:59,220 --> 00:21:59,850
Yang ini?

362
00:21:59,880 --> 00:22:00,920
Baiklah,

363
00:22:00,940 --> 00:22:02,310
pilihlah satu sendiri.

364
00:22:02,480 --> 00:22:03,050
Baiklah.

365
00:22:03,050 --> 00:22:04,530
Adakah ini kali pertama awak ke sini?

366
00:22:04,530 --> 00:22:05,500
Ya, ini kali pertama saya di sini.

367
00:22:05,500 --> 00:22:07,130
Sebelas dengan harga 10.

368
00:22:10,110 --> 00:22:11,180
Rumah Wanzhe

369
00:22:11,200 --> 00:22:14,260
berada di sudut jalan membeli-belah
