masa kau mabuk malam tu?

438
00:27:13,270 --> 00:27:14,710
Saya tak mahu cederakan awak.

439
00:27:16,900 --> 00:27:18,630
Jadi awak tak ucap selamat tinggal pun?

440
00:27:21,470 --> 00:27:23,330
Kau rindukan orang tu masa tu.

441
00:27:23,690 --> 00:27:26,090
Awak nak lepaskan saya
juga kali ni?

442
00:27:30,380 --> 00:27:31,340
Awak dah selesai?

443
